  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Finally at 17th level, your chakra scalpel is akin to master crafted blades, when you would activate your chakra scalpel you may instead spend 5 charges to activate your <em><strong>Chakra Sabre</strong></em>. Your Chakra Sabre gains all the benefits of your Crehakra Scalpel with the following changes: </p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">• </span>Your Chakra Sabre deals Necrotic damage and ignores immunity and resistance.<br /><span style=\"font-size:16px\">• </span>When you deal damage with your Chakra Sabre to a creature's hit points, they take an equal amount of chakra damage. <br /><span style=\"font-size:16px\">• </span>Your Chakra Sabre gains the Reach 2 Property.</p><p>Additonally, when you score a critical hit using your Chakra Scalpel, and roll maximum damage on a damage die you may reroll that die adding the result to the total damage.</p>",
